<document xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns:z="http://www.ebi.ac.uk/z" source="Whatizit"><text><SENT sid="0" pm="."><plain>The association of <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0013080" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="">Down's syndrome</z:e> with <z:hpo ids='HP_0001915'>aplastic anemia</z:hpo> is extremely rare with only six such cases reported in world literature </plain></SENT>
<SENT sid="1" pm="."><plain>Herein, we report a child of <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0013080" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="">Down's syndrome</z:e> with <z:hpo ids='HP_0001876'>pancytopenia</z:hpo> and <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0151773" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome" abbrv="">hypocellular marrow</z:e> </plain></SENT>
<SENT sid="2" pm="."><plain>There was associated <z:hpo ids='HP_0000821'>hypothyroidism</z:hpo> and the <z:hpo ids='HP_0001876'>pancytopenia</z:hpo> resolved with <z:chebi fb="4" ids="30660">thyroxine</z:chebi> treatment </plain></SENT>
<SENT sid="3" pm="."><plain>The child made uneventful recovery </plain></SENT>
</text></document>